# @SuppressWarnings FORMATTING

## RULE
Comment BEFORE annotation, annotation on single line

## CORRECT
```java
// Comment explaining WHY
@SuppressWarnings("PMD.RuleName")
@SuppressWarnings({"PMD.Rule1", "PMD.Rule2"})
```

## WRONG
```java
@SuppressWarnings("PMD.RuleName") // Comment after
@SuppressWarnings(
        "PMD.RuleName") // Comment after
@SuppressWarnings({
    "PMD.Rule1", // Comment inside
    "PMD.Rule2"
})
```
